SUMMARY = "Current terminal is a 3713-byte IPC-rendered command widget with 8 hard-coded commands. Missing production requirements: command table/tokenizer, Z_UI_CMD_BRIDGE_DATA implementation, paged PKG protocol, 1280x800 terminal contract, pipe/redirection/syscalls, and real package resolver."
